<p>
    <%= @user.your_name%>
    <% if current_user.hunt_ids.present?%>
    You are up to level
    <%= current_user.hunts.ids.first%> 
    And Your Horses's stamina is currently
<%= current_user.hunt_progressions.first.horse_stamina%> 
